in campaign: 1938352623339610114 we see a warning of no active ad sets

It looks like your campaign might not have any active ad sets. Could you check if the ad sets are paused or if they have reached their end date? If everything seems fine and you're still seeing this warning, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
but we have them there and they say ready (others say active)

If your ad sets are showing as 'ready' or 'active' but you're still seeing a warning, it might be a technical issue. Double-check that your payment method is valid and associated with the account, as this can sometimes cause ads not to run. If everything seems correct and the issue persists, please reach out to adsupport@newsbreak.com for further help.
